fields.Title: OFFICE / PUNCHCLOCK AND PHONE
fields.Description: For ten cents you can attempt an interfacing WC and call to a video rental you used to rent films from.

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""*Something?* Listen, I can't help..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Something?* Listen, I can't help you." He sounds annoyed now. "If you need further assistance you can visit us on the corner of Voyager and Main. Are we done?"

fields.Title: You: ""My name is Raphaël Ambrosius Coste..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "My name is Raphaël Ambrosius Costeau. Do you have anything on my name?"

fields.Title: You: "I might try this again later."
fields.Dialogue Text: I might try this again later.

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "Nothing tricky about that. You just..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nothing tricky about that. You just *do*, *fail*, *repeat* until it works. All it takes is motivation and practice.

fields.Title: Punch Clock/Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: You: "Insert 10 cents."
fields.Dialogue Text: Insert 10 cents.

fields.Title: You: ""Oh, okay. Thanks.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, okay. Thanks."

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""If you can, return it to us on the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If you can, return it to us on the corner of Voyager and Main."

fields.Title: You: "What was all shit?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What was all shit?

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""No.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No."

fields.Title: Punch Clock/Payphone: "The already familiar cold touch of..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The already familiar cold touch of plastic welcomes you as you pick up the handset.

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""Here we are! You haven't rented an..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Here we are! You haven't rented anything in five years, but you still have a copy of *Blue Ocean Hell* from November '46. Wooh, not a fun film, that one."

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Undoubtedly, no."
fields.Dialogue Text: Undoubtedly, no.

fields.Title: Punch Clock/Payphone: "The payphone hangs mutely on the wa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The payphone hangs mutely on the wall. There isn't much more to do here.

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "The voice of a youngster on the oth..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The voice of a youngster on the other end sounds as enthusiastic as that of a man walking towards the gallows.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""That's enough for you today," the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's enough for you today," the lieutenant says quietly. "Let's conclude this call."

fields.Title: Shivers: "Tiny heels, tip-toeing down the roa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Tiny heels, tip-toeing down the road. Beautiful steps, light-footed, with a lifetime ahead of them. You look up and the air seems to grow darker.

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""Sir, I don't know. It's a video re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sir, I don't know. It's a video rental. Maybe you rent videos here?"

fields.Title: Empathy: "He thinks you're pulling a prank on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He thinks you're pulling a prank on him.

fields.Title: You: ""Can't we do it without my last nam..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Can't we do it without my last name? I can't really remember it."

fields.Title: You: "Quietly hang up the phone. [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: Quietly hang up the phone. [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: "Let your muscle memory dial a rando..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Let your muscle memory dial a random number.

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""Maybe you called to extend your re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Maybe you called to extend your rental period? Do you need to extend your rental period?"

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""Video Revachol is a 24 hour video..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Video Revachol is a 24 hour video rental. We rent eight and ten millimetre film for home use. This is Lemmy."

fields.Title: You: ""Do you know me?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you know me?"

fields.Title: You: ""My name is Harry Something. Do you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "My name is Harry Something. Do you have anything on my name?"

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["tc.harry"] == true  and  Variable["tc.du_bois"] == false  and  Variable["tc.name_full_harrier"] == false

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: "...a crackle, someone picks up! The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: ...a crackle, someone picks up! They say: "Video Revachol, 24 hour video rental. We rent eight- and ten-millimetre film for home use. This is Lemmy, how may I help you?"

fields.Title: You: ""My name is Harry Du Bois. Do you h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "My name is Harry Du Bois. Do you have anything on my name?"

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["tc.harry"]  and  Variable["tc.du_bois"]  and  Variable["tc.name_full_harrier"] == false

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: "He concludes: "No wonder no one's b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He concludes: "No wonder no one's been missing it. Still, it would be great if you could return it to us. We're on the corner of Voyager and Main."

fields.Title: Punch Clock/Payphone: "An imposing combination of a punch-..."
fields.Dialogue Text: An imposing combination of a punch-clock and a payphone is looking down at you from the wall. A note on the side says: "Tokens unavailable due to strike. Use change."

fields.Title: You: ""Why did I call you?" (Continue.)"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why did I call you?" (Continue.)

fields.Title: Interfacing: "It's unclear whether you actually h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's unclear whether you actually have muscle memory. Right now your finger is just drawing vaguely occult patterns in the air.

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""Raphaël *what*? Listen, I can't he..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Raphaël *what*? Listen, I can't help you over the phone." He sounds annoyed now. "If you need further assistance you can visit us on the corner of Voyager and Main. Are we done?"

fields.Title: Punch Clock/Payphone: "The machine swallows your coin and..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The machine swallows your coin and seems to be waiting for your next move.

fields.Title: You: "Useful patterns?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Useful patterns?

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""If you need any further assistance..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If you need any further assistance you can visit us on the corner of Voyager and Main." He sounds annoyed now. "I can't help you over the phone -- are we done?"

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Your fingers run over the dial pad...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your fingers run over the dial pad. 005... that's the dialling code for Revachol -- 49-52... and a moment of hesitation before entering the final numbers: 993.

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""Let me fire up the machine..." Key..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let me fire up the machine..." Keys are being pressed in the background. "Du Bois... Du Bois..."

fields.Title: You: ""We're done." Hang up the phone. [L..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We're done." Hang up the phone. [Leave.]

fields.Title: Punch Clock/Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""What did you say your last name wa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What did you say your last name was?"

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""Uh... it's not an easy watch." He..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uh... it's not an easy watch." He reads: "'After the death of his daughter and subsequent divorce, Zsiemsk immigrant Igidius Wójcik tries to come to terms with the onset of dementia...'"

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Sure, why not. Muscle memory is a t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Sure, why not. Muscle memory is a tricky thing.

fields.Title: You: ""What kind of a film is that?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What kind of a film is that?"

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Suddenly you feel like you don't wa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Suddenly you feel like you don't want to hear about video rentals anymore. You don't want to hear about *any of it*. It was all shit. It's over.

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: ""What is this place?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What is this place?"

fields.Title: You: ""My name is Harrier Du Bois. Do you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "My name is Harrier Du Bois. Do you have anything on my name?"

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: ""Listen, man, I can't help you with..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Listen, man, I can't help you without your surname." He sounds annoyed now. "If you need further assistance you can visit us on the corner of Voyager and Main. Are we done?"

fields.Title: You: ""Maybe, but I don't even know my *n..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Maybe, but I don't even know my *name*."

fields.Title: You: ""No, I meant what is this place to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, I meant what is this place to *me*?"

fields.Title: Video Revachol, 24h: "The call is terminated by the other..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The call is terminated by the other party. You're left with the discomforting sound of the disconnect tone.

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, I feel sad about Video Revach..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, I feel sad about Video Revachol 24h."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "*It*."
fields.Dialogue Text: *It*.

fields.Title: Shivers: "On the corner of Voyager and Main a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: On the corner of Voyager and Main a large neon sign hangs on the side of a building: "Video Revachol, 24h." It's raining and there is almost no traffic on the street. A woman's footprints in the mud lead away from the front door.

fields.Title: Punch Clock/Payphone: "Still calling... then..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Still calling... then...

fields.Title: You: ""Something.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Something."
